RelatedSentence: On the first day of early voting for the May 27 runoff election , Lt. Gov. David Dewhurst cast a ballot for himself Monday for re-election as the candidate with the experience and character for the job , he said .

On the first day of early voting for the May 27 runoff election , Lt. Gov. David Dewhurst cast a ballot for himself Monday for re-election as the candidate with the experience and character for the job , he said .

But Dewhurst said he did n't know whether a raft of Republican rival Dan Patrick 's psychiatric records from the 1980 s that were released last week suggest that the Houston state senator was in any way unfit to serve .
